# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VeilLend Web — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values for your environment.
#
#   cp .env.example .env.local
#
# Variables prefixed with NEXT_PUBLIC_ are exposed to the browser bundle.
# Never put secrets or private keys in NEXT_PUBLIC_ variables.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


# ── Stellar Network ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Which Stellar network to connect to.
# Accepted values: "testnet" | "mainnet" | "futurenet"
# Default: testnet
NEXT_PUBLIC_STELLAR_NETWORK=testnet

# Horizon REST API endpoint for the chosen network.
# Testnet:  https://horizon-testnet.stellar.org
# Mainnet:  https://horizon.stellar.org
# Default: https://horizon-testnet.stellar.org
NEXT_PUBLIC_HORIZON_URL=https://horizon-testnet.stellar.org

# Stellar network passphrase — must match the network above exactly.
# Testnet:  Test SDF Network ; September 2015
# Mainnet:  Public Global Stellar Network ; September 2015
# Default: Test SDF Network ; September 2015
NEXT_PUBLIC_STELLAR_NETWORK_PASSPHRASE=Test SDF Network ; September 2015


# ── Backend / Indexer API ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Base URL for the VeilLend indexer / backend API.
# In local development this is the NestJS dev server.
# Default: http://localhost:3001
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Notes
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# • All four variables above have safe built-in defaults so the app starts on
#   testnet without any configuration. Set them explicitly in .env.local when
#   you need a different network or a remote API.
#
# • For production deployments set NEXT_PUBLIC_STELLAR_NETWORK=mainnet and
#   update NEXT_PUBLIC_HORIZON_URL and NEXT_PUBLIC_STELLAR_NETWORK_PASSPHRASE
#   to the corresponding mainnet values.
#
# • .env.local is git-ignored. Never commit actual credentials or secrets.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
